node.text:
Winning a Bassmaster Classic requires three days of execution, bait selection and sometimes an area of the lake all to yourself. In 2021, @hankcherryfishing displayed a few of those as he utilized a couple different lures and select areas to win at Lake Ray Roberts. 

Cherry used the brand new  @BerkleyFishing  Stunna jerkbait he designed as well as a key bait change late on Day 3 when he chose to flip with a Berkley Pit Boss. 
#Bassmaster #BassmasterClassic #BassFishing

node.title: Two lures that helped Hank Cherry win back-to-back Classics

#Bassmaster #BASSElite #BassFishing
